import React from 'react'
import tailwind from 'tailwind-rn'
import { Button, Image, StyleSheet, Text, View } from 'react-native'
import { Card } from '../components/card';
import { useNavigation } from '@react-navigation/native';
import Hr from '../components/hr';
import TimeLineIcon from '../components/svgs/TimeLineIcon'
import MoneyDollarCircleLineIcon from '../components/svgs/MoneyDollarCircleLineIcon';
import MapPinLineIcon from '../components/svgs/MapPinLineIcon';


export default function Vagas() {
    const navigation = useNavigation();
    return (
        <View style={tailwind("m-2")}>
            <Text style={tailwind("text-center text-xl mt-4 mb-6")}>Vagas</Text>
            <Card>
                <View style={tailwind("flex-row")}>
                    <Image source={{uri: "http://conexaovagasapi.ddns.net:52525/api/Empresa/Img/1050"}}
                           style={{ width: 30, height: 30 }}></Image>
                    <Text style={tailwind("ml-5")}>Estagiário Flutter</Text>
                </View>
                <Hr style={tailwind("my-2")}/>
                <View style={tailwind("flex-row")}>
                    <View style={tailwind("w-1/2")}>
                        <View style={tailwind("flex-row")}>
                            <MoneyDollarCircleLineIcon/>
                            <Text> R$ 1000</Text>
                        </View>
                        <View style={tailwind("flex-row")}>
                            <MapPinLineIcon style={tailwind("flex-none")}/>
                            <Text> Rua Barão de Campinas, São Paulo, SP</Text>
                        </View>
                        <View style={tailwind("flex-row")}>
                            <TimeLineIcon/>
                            <Text> 09/11/2020</Text>
                        </View>


                    </View>
                    <View style={tailwind("w-1/2")}>Lado B</View>
                </View>
            </Card>
        </View>
    )
}

const styles = StyleSheet.create({})
